   FLX Provider Registration
   _______________________________________________________________________

   As a training and education provider, the sooner you sign up for FLX
   services the better! Once you've posted information about your
   offerings on FLX, you're part of the nation's largest career
   development network featuring America's Job Bank, America's Talent Bank
   and America's Career InfoNet and America's Learning eXchange. These
   sites are visited by more than 13 million employers, job seekers and
   individual learners every week. Now that's traffic!
   Who ?              Who should register with FLX?
   Why ?              Six compelling reasons why you should become part of
   FLX now.
   How ?              A quick overview of FLX's fast and flexible
   registration process
                           which has been in use in FLX.
   Help ?              Step by Step Instructions.
   Setting up your FLX account
     __________________________________________________________________

   Click here to view the required information to complete your
   registration.
   If you are a valid ALX provider and you have a current contract with a
   federal agency to provide training, or if you are on appropriate GSA
   schedule you DO NOT need to complete this form. Just click here to copy
   your data from ALX
     __________________________________________________________________

      Enter a username : (7 - 15 characters or digits) ________________
     Choose a password : (7 - 15 characters or digits) ________________
             Re-enter password for confirmation ________________
        Enter a hint for your password in case you forget (optional)
                          ________________________

   Please write down your username and password & keep them in a safe
   place.
   You will need to login to your FLX account to enter & update
   information about the products or services you offer

